// n8n/build-f05-workflow.py. Body below is pasted VERBATIM (only the trailing
// `module.exports` block is stripped -- n8n's sandbox does not define `module`).
// Zero LLM: pure arithmetic over score_formulas.config -- design.md SS8.2's whole
